{"tid":1693682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（連登巴絲再入嚟）關於連登討論區嘅問卷調查上線啦！","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T11:16:38.000Z","uid":58727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22a782a498e87b11f1bd7a5d8d39f3489e3dd2af","tid":1693682,"uid":58727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"之前因為一啲技術問題, 令到我哋要由頭收集過回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋好需要大家幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我哋係一班讀緊中大新聞系嘅碩士生，而家做緊一個關於連登（LIHKG）討論區嘅使用與區議會選舉嘅關係嘅調查。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><a href=\"https://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVceSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=107d4e88\" target=\"_blank\">https://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR</a></strong></span><br />\n誠邀各位年滿十八歲，有使用「連登」（LIHKG）討論區的人填一份問卷（需時約5分鐘），萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是次研究唔會為閣下提供任何利益，但所搜集到嘅數據將對研究工作提供寶貴嘅資料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（閣下的參與純屬自願性質。閣下享有充分的權利在任何時候決定退出這項研究， 不會因此引致任何不良後果。凡有關閣下的資料將會保密，一切資料的編碼只有研究人員得悉，並會在研究完成後悉數銷毀。如閣下想獲得更多有關這項研究的資料，請以電郵(1155134419@link.cuhk.edu.hk)與本工作組成員聯絡。）<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手填份問卷吖~ 我哋嘅研究好需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後記得再廣傳畀親朋好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n新link在此</span></strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR%20&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVceSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=9ef1d5c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR </a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12573939486bc5af0a2cdcbfffb484ec67fe7f4","tid":1693682,"uid":58727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22a782a498e87b11f1bd7a5d8d39f3489e3dd2af","tid":1693682,"uid":58727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"之前因為一啲技術問題, 令到我哋要由頭收集過回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋好需要大家幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=