廣傳畀親朋好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n新link在此</span></strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR%20&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVceSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=9ef1d5c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_77IpCEfDj7KbUkR </a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:50:23.000Z","msg":"自推x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb76650feb14d76a0e322b2414e77eb5e5e8a86a","tid":1693682,"uid":94344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZwcWhx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZwcWhx.jpg&h=f252a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長期罷工效果<br />\n<br />\n返shift，射波齊參與<br />\n邊日<span style=\"color: red;\">放假</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">射波</span> 就好去遊客旺區振興經濟啦<img src=\"/